  "body": "Maybe rework **GasLimitRangeAndDeltaValidationRule** we have the same code on **AbstractBlockCreator**. We need this code to multiply the gaslimit by the slackCoefficient on fork block. we need to use a specific gasLimitCalculator fot that (ex **LongonGasLimitCalculator**)\n\n**Step :** \n 1)  Move the TargetingGasLimitCalculator to the same package as AbstractGasLimitSpecification \n 2) Rename TargetingGasLimitCalculator to FrontierTargetingGasLimitCalculator  \n 3) Create a LondonTargetingGasLimitCalculator\n 4) Define the valid TargetingGasLimitCalculator depends on the milestone on the protocolSpec and not on the BesuControllerBuilder (this class already contains the protocolSpec)\n\n**Example of code to change :** \n```java\n if (eip1559.isPresent() && eip1559.get().isForkBlock(header.getNumber())) {\n    parentGasLimit = parent.getGasLimit() * eip1559.get().getFeeMarket().getSlackCoefficient();\n  }\n```\n",
